  &lt;Comment&gt;
    &lt;CommentText&gt;Thank you for taking the time to feedback as we welcome comments to monitor and improve our services.

We would like to apologise you were disappointed with the availability of your results and that you had to chase these up on a couple of occasions. 

We hope we can assure you that the Trust strives to provide patients with excellent care and experience and so have forwarded your review to the Senior Management Team. These will be filtered down to the appropriate department to be discussed at their next team meeting.

If you continue to have concerns regarding this episode of care, we would encourage you to contact our Patient Advice and Liaison Service (PALS) at your earliest opportunity on telephone 0161 206 2003 or email pals@srft.nhs.uk quoting that you have been advised to do so via the NHS Website, so we can discuss and address the matters expressed in your review.


Kind regards
The Patient Experience Team
